R\left(t\right)=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
\cos2\pi t & \sin2\pi t & 0\\
-\sin2\pi t & \cos2\pi t & 0\\
0 & 0 & 1
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

这个路径不能连续的变为恒元，尝试一下，找一个
\begin_inset Formula $R\left(t,u\right)$
\end_inset

令
\begin_inset Formula $R\left(t,0\right)=R\left(t\right)$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $R\left(t,1\right)=\symbb{1}$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

